<FIELD name="_RAJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.ra" ref="J2000" datatype="double" width="10" precision="6" unit="deg"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_RA" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Right ascension (FK5, Equinox=J2000.0) at Epoch=J2000, proper motions taken into account </DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="_DEJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.dec" ref="J2000" datatype="double" width="10" precision="6" unit="deg"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_DEC" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Declination (FK5, Equinox=J2000.0) at Epoch=J2000, proper motions taken into account </DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="recno" ucd="meta.record" datatype="int" width="8" type="hidden"><!-- ucd="RECORD" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Record number assigned by the VizieR team. Should Not be used for identification.</DESCRIPTION>
<DESCRIPTION>[1/9110]+ Harvard Revised Number = Bright Star Number</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="RAJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.ra;meta.main" ref="J2000_2000.000" datatype="char" arraysize="10" xtype="hms"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_RA_MAIN" -->
<FIELD name="DEJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.dec;meta.main" ref="J2000_2000.000" datatype="char" arraysize="9" xtype="dms"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_DEC_MAIN" -->
<FIELD name="Vmag" ucd="phot.mag;em.opt.V" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_V" -->
<FIELD name="B-V" ucd="phot.color;em.opt.B;em.opt.V" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_B-V" -->
<DESCRIPTION>? B-V color in the UBV system</DESCRIPTION>
